{"tid":716812,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"[LensCulture] Street Photography Awards 2018","createTime":"2018-06-25T14:51:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-27T11:39:44.000Z","uid":38218,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"58e441585bb75871a63ed5c8ab2d3fd6643ecb48","tid":716812,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T14:51:58.000Z","msg":"上星期<br />\n第四屆LensCulture Street Photography Awards宣佈賽果<br />\n參加者來自世界名地多達170個國家<br />\n作品題材涉獵由東京的富有未來感的都市景色<br />\n以至柏林的黑白題材<br />\n亦包括印度和法國的臨時城市居所、<br />\n<br />\nLensCulture:<br />\n&ldquo;How do we define street photography? <br />\nFor those with a tendency toward classical photography, <br />\nthe romantic black-and-white photographs of Henri Cartier-Bresson may come to mind. <br />\nAnd yet, the genre of street photography has opened up quite a bit in this global age&mdash;<br />\nphotography is at the center of our &ldquo;always-on,&rdquo; interconnected lives.&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n&quot;A good photograph needs three things: <br />\na clear authorial &lsquo;voice&rsquo;, a coherent, well-conceived subject and <br />\nthe skill to craft the image well.&quot; <br />\nby Alasdair Foster (one of the jury members)<br />\n<br />\n首名 photo series<br />\nSOWRAV DAS<br />\nFloating Heroes<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/NiX0PHJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FNiX0PHJ.jpg&h=ef5d03d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/1tXED5R.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F1tXED5R.jpg&h=af0f13fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mhQAecM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FmhQAecM.jpg&h=a5706cec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n呢輯相題材主要講一班係印度有一群工人<br />\n因各種原因<br />\n而需在街頭作息<br />\n<br />\n次名 photo series<br />\nİLKER KARAM<br />\nTurkey<br />\nIn Pursuit of Myself<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/MEowqIO.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FMEowqIO.jpg&h=da3e7528&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8RphkEz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8RphkEz.jpg&h=2591f52e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/wRnlH4k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FwRnlH4k.jpg&h=94efa5b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n第三名 photo series<br />\nCOCOA LANEY<br />\nItaly<br />\nGaps<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/d4XJiCD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fd4XJiCD.jpg&h=a11cd9f5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/8e44PnP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F8e44PnP.jpg&h=e65bc61a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/QTduyjM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FQTduyjM.jpg&h=3c984316&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"077082d1879ce763936ce96a89bcc3582ab0bb15","tid":716812,"uid":38218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"Single image winners<br />\n首名<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oHJpELj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FoHJpELj.jpg&h=82a81b77&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMACIEJ DAKOWICZ<br />\nBeach Scene, Chaung Tha, Myanmar<br />\n<br />\n次名<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/k6mGAwb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fk6mGAwb.jpg&h=c0846d70&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nBARRY TALIS<br />\nFrom &quot;The Flow of Spirit&quot;<br />\n<br />\n第三名<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/RMKzs2A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FRMKzs2A.jpg&h=03311c58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nJINGSHENG NIE<br />\nHanging Pig"},{"pid":"434840b3ff325dc43ae6822da5e6c171ed3bc612","tid":716812,"uid":38218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T14:53:51.000Z","msg":"評審特選<br />\n原先呢七張都各有不同評審的comment<br />\n但我對部分的意見有保留<br />\n所以唔post 係度<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4pzWvVM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4pzWvVM.jpg&h=45f6e38e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/t5xmnOm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ft5xmnOm.jpg&h=4f7feca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/OHcCRk8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FOHcCRk8.jpg&h=4f3d2e9b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/f6P5qmC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Ff6P5qmC.jpg&h=3f77e9ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/rDuu0hW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2FrDuu0hW.jpg&h=0f053053&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDAVID ALAN HARVEY (評審): <br />\nThis photograph by Niki Gleoudi is magically mysterious, sensuous, and graphic. <br />\nNiki has a whole series on beach life, and this is one of her best. <br />\nIt is not pedantic nor condescendingly descriptive, which would render it boring. That is the beauty of this image.<br />\nWe are not quite sure of the relationship between the two men, yet there is an implied intimacy and affection. <br />\nThe layered juxtaposition of the unicorn float and the boat in the background allows our eye to travel around inside the picture, yet keeps us circling back to the man in the foreground. As today&rsquo;s astute photographers often embrace a visceral visual literacy, Niki hits the mark.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/4MoXahy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F4MoXahy.jpg&h=20e6dca3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nALASDAIR FOSTER (評審): <br />\nThis image brings an interesting new point of view <br />\nfrom which to consider the life of the city street. <br />\nWhile shooting from overhead is not, in itself, new, <br />\nthe searing lateral light has rendered the shadows more explicitly familiar than the figures themselves. <br />\nThis creates an ambiguity, since the image appears to exist simultaneously in two different perspectives. <br />\nThe cobbled patterns of the piazza set the figures into a highly idiosyncratic field, which the colorful geometric forms of the rectilinear awnings and curving garden disturb and animate the edge of the frame, energizing the whole.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/r07cl3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2Fr07cl3a.jpg&h=ffdee231&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.lensculture.com/2018-lensculture-street-photography-award-winners\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.lensculture.com%2F2018-lensculture-street-photography-award-winners&d=6u3WKRALOrPV2yHo7Ghbi%2FiMucz1dB5Ms3PJ3VCnrF8%3D&h=e369e9bf\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.lensculture.com/2018-lensculture-street-photography-award-winners</a>"},{"pid":"2e3d64ad06c1c849e6f8f7a253b83f9cfeb2386e","tid":716812,"uid":67041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T23:50:11.000Z","msg":"次名第一張好正"},{"pid":"2239e66615fa96ff3c44e52ed50291a9c0fcf798","tid":716812,"uid":40061,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-26T00:05:36.000Z","msg":"Single image 故事性 2&gt;1 啦"},{"pid":"2e226ef2f79f2c9ff3f2261431ca403a7d807b99","tid":716812,"uid":4279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"077082d1879ce763936ce96a89bcc3582ab0bb15","tid":716812,"uid":38218,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-25T14:52:11.000Z","msg":"Single image winners<br />\n首名<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/oHJpELj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"